Comment: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,845年
Comment: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因突然出現的超大型巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,和盔甲巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一切的日常與牆壁一同被摧毀
Comment: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類放棄了瑪利亞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失去了兩成的人口以及三分之一的領土
Comment: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類活動範圍退至羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,850年
Comment: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因再次現身的超大型巨人 城牆被破壞
Comment: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類又再次地允許了巨人的進攻
Comment: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士兵們接二連三地在巨人的面前倒下
Comment: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後...
Comment: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點!
Comment: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,曾一度成為了巨人飼料的艾連．葉卡
Comment: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又再次地 從謎之巨人的身體中現身
Comment: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,集合!!
Comment: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,南側領土最高負責人
Comment: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,達特．皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看上在戰鬥中巨人化的艾連．葉卡的力量而下達某個決定
Comment: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,變成巨人後的他
Comment: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將會抬起前門附近的那顆大岩石
Comment: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,搬到被破壞的門旁
Comment: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將洞口封住
Comment: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當這次作戰成功之時
Comment: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類將會是首次成功從巨人手中把領土給搶回來
Comment: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這一步
Comment: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將會是我們人類
Comment: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,偉大的進擊!!
Comment: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是這個作戰才剛開始
Comment: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就隨即面臨失敗
Comment: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,勉強讓大部分的巨人聚集到城市的角落了
Comment: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然盡力避免了戰鬥
Comment: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但還是失去了大約兩成的士兵
Comment: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是失去了
Comment: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士兵不是自己去送死
Comment: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是因為我的命令而死的
Comment: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在是關係到人類存亡的關鍵
Comment: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果是為了讓人類存活下去的話
Comment: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使被稱為殺戮者 我也無所謂
Comment: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿卡曼!!
Comment: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂! 阿卡曼別去!
Comment: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快離開他!
Comment: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連 你不認識我了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你的...
Comment: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,家人!
Comment: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你必須用那顆岩石把洞口封住!
Comment: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作戰失敗了
Comment: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就知道
Comment: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,根本就沒有秘密武器這回事
Comment: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連 你是人類!
Comment: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是...
Comment: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,閃開 阿卡曼!!
Comment: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙是怎樣
Comment: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過是個腦袋不怎麼好的巨人嘛
Comment: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊安班長
Comment: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前門有兩個接近
Comment: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,分別是10公尺級跟6公尺級!
Comment: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,後方也有一個
Comment: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,12公尺級的巨人正往這裡接近!!
Comment: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊安 該撤退了!
Comment: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那小夥子根本沒辦法堵住那個洞
Comment: 0,0:05:58.51,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊
Comment: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒辦法了 把他留在這裡吧
Comment: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發現精銳小組施放的紅色信號彈!
Comment: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來封鎖作戰發生了很嚴重的問題
Comment: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,白白去送死
Comment: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,同伴們...
Comment: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,根本就是白白去送死
Comment: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 快看那個
Comment: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼? 怎麼了!
Comment: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失敗了嗎...?
Comment: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂! 阿爾敏你要去哪?
Comment: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯司令
Comment: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該要立刻恢復成防衛大門的狀態
Comment: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,您意下如何?
Comment: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不需要
Comment: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請下令精銳小組撤退...
Comment: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒必要
Comment: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,繼續讓巨人聚集到角落來
Comment: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,關於精銳小組的話
Comment: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經全權交給他們在現場處理了
Comment: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們不只是本事高強
Comment: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是背負著人類命運的最精銳
Comment: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不容許他們如此輕易就認輸
Comment: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了不讓死去的士兵們白白犧牲
Comment: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,凡是能夠嘗試的事都給我做到底
Comment: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 你在猶豫什麼?
Comment: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點指揮啊!
Comment: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊安 這又不是你的錯!
Comment: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這原本就是毫無意義的作戰
Comment: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家都很清楚!
Comment: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然有嘗試的價值
Comment: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過我們做得夠多了!
Comment: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽好了!
Comment: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們班要爬上牆去!
Comment: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,慢著!
Comment: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等一下...
Comment: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冷靜點 阿卡曼
Comment: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,里柯班
Comment: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,去對付後方12公尺級的!
Comment: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米塔比班和我這一班去對付前面那兩隻!
Comment: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說什麼?
Comment: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被賦予指揮權的人是我!
Comment: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我閉嘴遵從命令
Comment: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不能丟下毫無防備的葉卡
Comment: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作戰計畫改變了
Comment: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,直到回收葉卡為止
Comment: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,保護他免於遭受巨人的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他對人類來說是一個珍貴的可能性
Comment: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並不是可以這麼簡單就捨去的東西
Comment: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為他和我們不同
Comment: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有人能夠取代他
Comment: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了那個失控的人類兵器
Comment: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明光是這次就有數百人死了
Comment: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道將他回收後要再讓同樣的狀況重演嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯...
Comment: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不管犧牲多少人 都應該要不斷地挑戰!
Comment: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連他怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏自己一個人往那邊去了
Comment: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想應該是沒事吧
Comment: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該?
Comment: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定沒事的
Comment: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連他做得到
Comment: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將巨人聚集到城市的角落
Comment: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只覺得是浪費時間
Comment: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以巨人為對手的戰鬥一定會變成消耗戰
Comment: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在目前的階段
Comment: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是想避免士兵的陣亡吧?
Comment: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,意思是在現在這個階段死去的士兵是白白送死?
Comment: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,遲早會變成一場大戰的!
Comment: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了那個時候的到來
Comment: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而儲備兵力將犧牲降低至最小限度是理所當然的
Comment: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上頭是正確的
Comment: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是這樣嗎?
Comment: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是這樣!
Comment: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,既然如此 那就以將犧牲降至最小來行動吧
Comment: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們彼此都是
Comment: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊安你瘋了嗎？
Comment: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼妳告訴我人類要怎麼樣才能戰勝巨人啊?
Comment: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,里柯 妳說啊!
Comment: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要怎麼做才能夠突破目前的狀況
Comment: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能保住人類的本性!
Comment: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且還可以不必死!
Comment: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,戰勝巨人那壓倒性的力量!
Comment: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要如何才能辦到?
Comment: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要如何戰勝巨人...
Comment: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我怎麼可能會知道...
