Comment: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不要再有人因為我而死了
Comment: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡 在這種時候故障
Comment: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰!
Comment: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼不使用立體機動裝置?
Comment: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道!
Comment: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,故障了嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總會有辦法啦!
Comment: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,畜生!
Comment: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我在扯人後腿是怎樣
Comment: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有什麼辦法了嗎...
Comment: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們不是說好總有一天要去外面的世界探險嗎?
Comment: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在牆外很遙遠的地方
Comment: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有著會燃燒的水
Comment: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冰凍的大地
Comment: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還有一望無際的沙的雪原
Comment: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是我的爸爸與媽媽試圖想去的世界
Comment: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,或許你已經忘記了
Comment: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你之所以不再提起那些
Comment: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不就是因為不想讓我加入調查軍團嗎?
Comment: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,外面的...世界...
Comment: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回答我
Comment: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一旦走出牆外
Comment: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明就是個地獄般的世界
Comment: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有可能像我爸媽一樣
Comment: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以悽慘的死法死去
Comment: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼艾連還是想去外面的世界呢?
Comment: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你問我為什麼?
Comment: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這還需要你問嗎?
Comment: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為我 就是出生在這世界上的啊!
Comment: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:24:03.55,0:24:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,去吧 跑吧 生存下去吧
Comment: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在許多的話語交錯及眾多生命凋零而去的戰場上
Comment: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連背起希望
Comment: 0,0:24:14.59,0:24:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,朝向城門
