Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}845年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因突然出現的超大型巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}和盔甲巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一切的日常與牆壁一同被摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類放棄了瑪利亞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}失去了兩成的人口以及三分之一的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類活動範圍退至羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}850年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因再次現身的超大型巨人 城牆被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類又再次地允許了巨人的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士兵們接二連三地在巨人的面前倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}曾一度成為了巨人飼料的艾連．葉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又再次地 從謎之巨人的身體中現身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}集合!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}南側領土最高負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}達特．皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看上在戰鬥中巨人化的艾連．葉卡的力量而下達某個決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}變成巨人後的他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將會抬起前門附近的那顆大岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}搬到被破壞的門旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將洞口封住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}當這次作戰成功之時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類將會是首次成功從巨人手中把領土給搶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將會是我們人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}偉大的進擊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是這個作戰才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就隨即面臨失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}勉強讓大部分的巨人聚集到城市的角落了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然盡力避免了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但還是失去了大約兩成的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不是失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士兵不是自己去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為我的命令而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在是關係到人類存亡的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果是為了讓人類存活下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即使被稱為殺戮者 我也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿卡曼!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂! 阿卡曼別去!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快離開他!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 你不認識我了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}家人!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你必須用那顆岩石把洞口封住!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作戰失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}根本就沒有秘密武器這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 你是人類!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}閃開 阿卡曼!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過是個腦袋不怎麼好的巨人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}伊安班長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前門有兩個接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}分別是10公尺級跟6公尺級!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}後方也有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}12公尺級的巨人正往這裡接近!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}伊安 該撤退了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那小夥子根本沒辦法堵住那個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒辦法了 把他留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}發現精銳小組施放的紅色信號彈!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看來封鎖作戰發生了很嚴重的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}白白去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}同伴們...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}根本就是白白去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 快看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼? 怎麼了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}失敗了嗎...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂! 阿爾敏你要去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯司令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該要立刻恢復成防衛大門的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}您意下如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請下令精銳小組撤退...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}繼續讓巨人聚集到角落來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}關於精銳小組的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我已經全權交給他們在現場處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們不只是本事高強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是背負著人類命運的最精銳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不容許他們如此輕易就認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了不讓死去的士兵們白白犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}凡是能夠嘗試的事都給我做到底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 你在猶豫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點指揮啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}伊安 這又不是你的錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這原本就是毫無意義的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家都很清楚!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然有嘗試的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過我們做得夠多了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們班要爬上牆去!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}慢著!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜點 阿卡曼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里柯班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}去對付後方12公尺級的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米塔比班和我這一班去對付前面那兩隻!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被賦予指揮權的人是我!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我閉嘴遵從命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不能丟下毫無防備的葉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作戰計畫改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}直到回收葉卡為止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}保護他免於遭受巨人的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他對人類來說是一個珍貴的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並不是可以這麼簡單就捨去的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為他和我們不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有人能夠取代他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了那個失控的人類兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明光是這次就有數百人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道將他回收後要再讓同樣的狀況重演嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不管犧牲多少人 都應該要不斷地挑戰!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連他怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏自己一個人往那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想應該是沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連他做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將巨人聚集到城市的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我只覺得是浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以巨人為對手的戰鬥一定會變成消耗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在目前的階段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是想避免士兵的陣亡吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}意思是在現在這個階段死去的士兵是白白送死?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}遲早會變成一場大戰的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了那個時候的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而儲備兵力將犧牲降低至最小限度是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}上頭是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是這樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}既然如此 那就以將犧牲降至最小來行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們彼此都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}伊安你瘋了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼妳告訴我人類要怎麼樣才能戰勝巨人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里柯 妳說啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要怎麼做才能夠突破目前的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能保住人類的本性!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且還可以不必死!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰勝巨人那壓倒性的力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要如何才能辦到?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要如何戰勝巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我怎麼可能會知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以我們現在該做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只剩下這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了這個還搞不清楚的人類兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只能拼了我們的老命去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}完成任務!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很悲慘對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們人類唯一能做的竟然是這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好了 該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是我們能夠進行的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是我們被賦予的垂死掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那種事情 我無法認同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂! 里柯!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會遵從作戰行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我覺得你所說得沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會讓他們知道被逼到絕境的人類的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為我無法認同自己是白白去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}後面的12公尺級就交給我們班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走吧! 我們還要應付前面那兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}謝謝你 伊安班長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿卡曼...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無須道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不知道妳會做出什麼事 所以捏了把冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過妳可以依照當初的作戰自由行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那樣才能發揮妳的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}畢竟妳是為了保護男朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是家人...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}破損的地方沒有修復
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為之前的傷嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對艾連的影響呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再說 有辦法保證艾連可以恢復原貌嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}算了...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這不是我自己隨便想想就能知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在我只能做我自己做得到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}究竟怎麼了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在... 到底在做什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我現在坐著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}今天是幾號了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這裡是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是家裡啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}睡覺吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在做什麼? 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽好了 總而言之就是讓巨人不要從那個角落離開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要專注於這一點 集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們沒有必要與巨人交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}訓練兵以三人一組在地上跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到了牆壁邊的話就往上面飛 千萬別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}萬一有漏掉的巨人就由我們來打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}萬一?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不是十分之一的機率嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們發現有危險的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}依照自己的判斷來行動也沒差嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果這樣可以成功的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}基爾休坦班出發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}糟糕... 後面!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有一個13公尺級朝著葉卡接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大門的方向陸續有新的巨人進來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大約是10公尺級的四個!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿卡曼 後面的麻煩妳了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別讓巨人接近葉卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這裡就要攔下來!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算是精銳 要兩個班同時對付4個巨人也太....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼巨人們都...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類的數目又不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道...是被艾連所吸引?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作戰如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連他到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很危險 你快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個巨人並沒有艾連的意志!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我對他說話也都沒有反應!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不管是誰來做都已經沒有意義了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作戰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}失敗了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為不能丟下艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以大家都在奮戰!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是再這麼下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人太多 可能會導致全軍覆沒!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從頭部後方到脖子...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}長1公尺!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}寬10公分!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要試著把艾連拖出來!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎妳別讓其他巨人靠近這裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你要幹嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連是從巨人的弱點部位出來的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個和巨人的本質之謎應該有所關連...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別擔心...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要避開正中央的部位!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不會死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}頂多就只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有點痛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏 你別亂來!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在只需做妳能做的事!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要米卡莎過去一定會有人能因此得救!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連就交給我 妳快去!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 你聽得見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你要振作啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果你不出來我們大家都會死的!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}千萬別輸給巨人的身體!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反正你快點就對了趕快離開這團肉塊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要我從這裡出來?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我現在...很睏啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你媽的仇不報了嗎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不是要把巨人殺光嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不是痛恨那些殺死你媽的傢伙嗎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在說什麼啊阿爾敏?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我媽就在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連! 艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快清醒過來啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在裡面吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果你繼續待在裡面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會被巨人殺死的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那樣的話一切都會在此結束!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我根本不知道你在說什麼 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼非要出去不可...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼一定要出去...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}幹嘛加入調查軍團...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即使不願意 也只能憑自己的判斷來行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}得手了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總算是倒下來了 可惡的傢伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}暫時保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿卡曼回來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}與米塔比班會合!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奇怪...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點去!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不要再有人因為我而死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡 在這種時候故障
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼不使用立體機動裝置?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}故障了嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總會有辦法啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}畜生!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我在扯人後腿是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有什麼辦法了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們不是說好總有一天要去外面的世界探險嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在牆外很遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有著會燃燒的水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冰凍的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還有一望無際的沙的雪原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是我的爸爸與媽媽試圖想去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}或許你已經忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你之所以不再提起那些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不就是因為不想讓我加入調查軍團嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}外面的...世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一旦走出牆外
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明就是個地獄般的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有可能像我爸媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以悽慘的死法死去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼艾連還是想去外面的世界呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你問我為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這還需要你問嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為我 就是出生在這世界上的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.55,0:24:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}去吧 跑吧 生存下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在許多的話語交錯及眾多生命凋零而去的戰場上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連背起希望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.59,0:24:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}朝向城門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
